{
    "publish_date": "2014-01-29T18:34:32.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT10M53S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "&quot;I&#39;m sorry you have to touch my face.", 
            "dur": "3.101", 
            "start": "10.298"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at this breakout; I look disgusting.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.256", 
            "start": "13.417"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I&#39;m sorry, but I am not a pretty woman.&quot;", 
            "dur": "6.27", 
            "start": "17.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;No. Thank you, but no.\nI look like crap.&quot;", 
            "dur": "5.942", 
            "start": "24.528"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;The doctor says\nthat I have to lose weight.", 
            "dur": "3.423", 
            "start": "31.424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, sorry. This is what\nyou gotta work with.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.163", 
            "start": "34.847"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;I look in the mirror, and\nall I see is a tired mom.", 
            "dur": "5.249", 
            "start": "38.894"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I see these wrinkles,\nand I feel old and ugly.&quot;", 
            "dur": "6.171", 
            "start": "44.143"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this is what I hear every single\nsolitary day of my life.", 
            "dur": "4.859", 
            "start": "52.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I am a makeup artist,\nand these are real words from real women.", 
            "dur": "5.606", 
            "start": "56.867"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m also an actress,\nbut for my past 7 years of doing makeup,", 
            "dur": "4.104", 
            "start": "62.473"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have discovered,", 
            "dur": "1.456", 
            "start": "66.577"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "within the first 3 seconds\nof sitting in my chair,", 
            "dur": "3.071", 
            "start": "68.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "almost every single woman apologizes\nto me for the way she looks.", 
            "dur": "4.993", 
            "start": "71.104"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Doesn&#39;t matter how young, how old,", 
            "dur": "2.321", 
            "start": "76.097"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what socioeconomic background\nshe comes from,", 
            "dur": "2.367", 
            "start": "78.418"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "how traditionally beautiful she is,", 
            "dur": "2.363", 
            "start": "80.785"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "almost every single woman apologizes\nand does not feel that she measures up", 
            "dur": "4.704", 
            "start": "83.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to this new standard of beauty.", 
            "dur": "3.727", 
            "start": "87.852"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m sure that maybe some of you\nmight be able to relate", 
            "dur": "3.022", 
            "start": "91.579"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to this apology thing?", 
            "dur": "2.082", 
            "start": "94.601"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I see some of you nodding.", 
            "dur": "2.026", 
            "start": "96.683"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, it just so happens", 
            "dur": "2.109", 
            "start": "98.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I was actually the makeup artist\nfor TEDx last year,", 
            "dur": "3.884", 
            "start": "100.818"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the same thing happened\nwhen these incredibly innovative women", 
            "dur": "3.371", 
            "start": "104.702"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sat in my chair.", 
            "dur": "1.624", 
            "start": "108.073"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They apologized.", 
            "dur": "2.574", 
            "start": "109.697"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, I have discovered that\nthere is a very small group of women", 
            "dur": "5.364", 
            "start": "112.271"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who don&#39;t apologize.", 
            "dur": "1.855", 
            "start": "117.635"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And these are the movers, the shakers,\nthey&#39;re the powerhouses.", 
            "dur": "3.061", 
            "start": "119.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They could be CEO&#39;s, or stay-at-home moms,", 
            "dur": "2.623", 
            "start": "122.551"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but they don&#39;t measure themselves\nby a mirror.", 
            "dur": "2.838", 
            "start": "125.174"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sure, they wear makeup,\nbut they don&#39;t apologize for it.", 
            "dur": "3.497", 
            "start": "128.012"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They live in the moment,", 
            "dur": "1.969", 
            "start": "131.509"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they let themselves have\nthat pleasure of living in the moment", 
            "dur": "4.291", 
            "start": "133.478"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and in the now.", 
            "dur": "1.239", 
            "start": "137.769"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I am in awe of these women.", 
            "dur": "2.551", 
            "start": "139.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s probably some of you\nvery rare, precious, confident creatures", 
            "dur": "4.727", 
            "start": "141.559"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in this audience.", 
            "dur": "1.506", 
            "start": "146.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to you ladies, I say go ahead\nand take a bathroom break!", 
            "dur": "4.086", 
            "start": "147.792"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can be back in like 5\u00bd minutes\nor something, because you don&#39;t need this!", 
            "dur": "3.851", 
            "start": "151.878"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You don&#39;t need to hear what I have to say.", 
            "dur": "2.518", 
            "start": "155.729"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the other women\nin this very small group", 
            "dur": "3.093", 
            "start": "158.247"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are the women who are aware\nof their own mortality.", 
            "dur": "5.17", 
            "start": "161.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;ll get back to them in a little bit.", 
            "dur": "2.576", 
            "start": "166.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, a woman will make\nan appointment with me", 
            "dur": "2.166", 
            "start": "169.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for a variety of different reasons.", 
            "dur": "1.723", 
            "start": "171.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A lot of times, she just feels down\nabout the way she looks,", 
            "dur": "2.921", 
            "start": "172.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and her friend will tell her, &quot;Oh,\nyou have to go see Eva, she&#39;s amazing.", 
            "dur": "3.141", 
            "start": "175.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She&#39;s great. She&#39;ll teach you\nmakeup tricks,", 
            "dur": "1.902", 
            "start": "179.037"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s going to change your life.&quot;", 
            "dur": "2.819", 
            "start": "180.939"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I have to be honest.", 
            "dur": "2.009", 
            "start": "183.758"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think that makeup\nis the very least of what I do.", 
            "dur": "4.623", 
            "start": "185.767"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;m not saying, denying,", 
            "dur": "1.588", 
            "start": "190.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that makeup does not play a very real part", 
            "dur": "2.447", 
            "start": "191.978"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in making a woman feel more attractive,\nand thus more confident,", 
            "dur": "4.211", 
            "start": "194.425"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because we&#39;re all aware", 
            "dur": "1.478", 
            "start": "198.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of those biological cues\nof attraction between human beings,", 
            "dur": "4.256", 
            "start": "200.114"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like symmetry, and color, and light.", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "204.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when we see them in ourselves\nor somebody else,", 
            "dur": "3.016", 
            "start": "207.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it pleases our primordial senses.", 
            "dur": "4.615", 
            "start": "210.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I, as a makeup artist,\nam very adept with the skills and tools", 
            "dur": "3.735", 
            "start": "215.551"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to very easily manipulate and enhance\nthose bio-cues on the face.", 
            "dur": "4.959", 
            "start": "219.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s my job.", 
            "dur": "2.242", 
            "start": "224.245"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;ll be honest with you.", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "226.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think every single woman\nwho sits in my chair", 
            "dur": "3.251", 
            "start": "229.077"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is beautiful with or without makeup.", 
            "dur": "4.052", 
            "start": "232.328"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She just has no idea!", 
            "dur": "4.342", 
            "start": "236.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is why I like to think of myself", 
            "dur": "2.428", 
            "start": "240.722"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as treading in the deep end\nof a shallow profession.", 
            "dur": "4.393", 
            "start": "243.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)", 
            "dur": "3.849", 
            "start": "247.543"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I use makeup as my tool\nto help her believe it.", 
            "dur": "6.752", 
            "start": "251.392"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Makeup is my therapy puppet", 
            "dur": "2.408", 
            "start": "258.144"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to help a woman open up\nabout how she&#39;s feeling,", 
            "dur": "3.347", 
            "start": "260.552"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and express to me what her concerns are,\nso I can address them.", 
            "dur": "4.345", 
            "start": "263.899"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you know what?\nIt works!", 
            "dur": "2.467", 
            "start": "268.244"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Almost every time, I see\na woman leap up out of my chair", 
            "dur": "4.76", 
            "start": "270.711"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with this new skip in her step.", 
            "dur": "1.833", 
            "start": "275.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I see her actually look in the mirror\nand actually smile at herself,", 
            "dur": "4.444", 
            "start": "277.304"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if it&#39;s temporary.", 
            "dur": "1.859", 
            "start": "281.748"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is a very real transformation\nthat happens in this chair.", 
            "dur": "5.33", 
            "start": "283.607"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh no. What are you talking about?\nI am not a pretty woman.", 
            "dur": "7.725", 
            "start": "293.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My mother-in-law says that\nI have a round face,", 
            "dur": "3.592", 
            "start": "301.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and there is no way to make\na round, fat face pretty.&quot;", 
            "dur": "5.236", 
            "start": "305.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I can&#39;t believe what I hear,\nbecause all I see is a beautiful woman.", 
            "dur": "6.405", 
            "start": "310.239"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I say, &quot;Matir, but look at your\ngorgeous, golden skin!", 
            "dur": "4.049", 
            "start": "316.644"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here, hold the mirror,\nwatch what I&#39;m doing.", 
            "dur": "1.925", 
            "start": "320.693"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at these perfect almond eyes,", 
            "dur": "4.032", 
            "start": "322.618"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these lips, my God,\nin my next life, I want these lips.", 
            "dur": "5.558", 
            "start": "326.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Your smile just lit up this room!&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.037", 
            "start": "332.208"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;You&#39;re right.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.353", 
            "start": "342.911"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, you would think\nbecause this is my job,", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "348.853"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I do this everyday,\nand I hear what women say,", 
            "dur": "2.115", 
            "start": "351.553"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and I have this unique perspective,", 
            "dur": "2.026", 
            "start": "353.668"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that I would be different.", 
            "dur": "2.673", 
            "start": "355.694"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But -- here&#39;s what happens\nwhen I sit in somebody&#39;s makeup chair.", 
            "dur": "6.307", 
            "start": "358.367"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Oh, God. I&#39;m sorry,\nI have a very tough face.", 
            "dur": "4.969", 
            "start": "364.674"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I hate that I am actually dependent\non eyeliner", 
            "dur": "3.675", 
            "start": "369.643"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to even walk out my front door.", 
            "dur": "2.472", 
            "start": "373.318"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, oh no, don&#39;t worry,\nmy nose is like a Muppet&#39;s fist.", 
            "dur": "6.019", 
            "start": "375.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just like ee, ee, erh.", 
            "dur": "2.547", 
            "start": "381.809"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, no worries trying to cover it up.&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.556", 
            "start": "384.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I have said those exact words\nin somebody else&#39;s makeup chair!", 
            "dur": "4.487", 
            "start": "387.912"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I, too, do not feel that I measure up,", 
            "dur": "3.261", 
            "start": "392.399"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or can hold up to this insane,\nnew measure of beauty in this world,", 
            "dur": "5.25", 
            "start": "395.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s like porn and fashion,\nand Photoshop, all mixed up in one.", 
            "dur": "4.571", 
            "start": "400.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Laughter)\n(Applause)", 
            "dur": "1.722", 
            "start": "405.481"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah. Good luck with that.", 
            "dur": "2.779", 
            "start": "407.203"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "(Applause)", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "409.982"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s not going away.\nSo what are we going to do?", 
            "dur": "4.136", 
            "start": "413.231"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What am I going to do\nto feel and appreciate what I have?", 
            "dur": "6.77", 
            "start": "417.367"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which brings me back to that other\nsmall group of women", 
            "dur": "3.402", 
            "start": "424.137"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that don&#39;t apologize.", 
            "dur": "2.052", 
            "start": "427.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh -- all right -- ah", 
            "dur": "3.061", 
            "start": "433.637"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;It&#39;s my birthday!", 
            "dur": "5.407", 
            "start": "438.274"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m 96 years old,\nand I&#39;m on borrowed time now, honey.", 
            "dur": "8.8", 
            "start": "443.681"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But, I think I look pretty good.&quot;", 
            "dur": "6.825", 
            "start": "452.481"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Ah, this feels so good,\nI&#39;m going to fall asleep.", 
            "dur": "5.088", 
            "start": "459.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yes, I have two little ones.\nTwo and four year old.", 
            "dur": "4.81", 
            "start": "464.394"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I just had a double mastectomy,\nand six rounds of chemo.", 
            "dur": "3.675", 
            "start": "469.204"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I&#39;m just so happy\nto be pampering myself.", 
            "dur": "3.623", 
            "start": "472.879"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I have to say, I love my new wig!&quot;", 
            "dur": "4.775", 
            "start": "476.502"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is this what it&#39;s going to take for me?", 
            "dur": "3.426", 
            "start": "481.277"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is this what it&#39;s going to take\nfor me to appreciate what I have?", 
            "dur": "4.495", 
            "start": "484.703"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "To be confronted with the prospect\nof illness or death?", 
            "dur": "4.248", 
            "start": "489.198"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is that what it&#39;s going to take for us\nto appreciate what we have?", 
            "dur": "3.557", 
            "start": "493.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, I&#39;m not going to take that.", 
            "dur": "3.574", 
            "start": "497.003"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don&#39;t accept it.", 
            "dur": "2.366", 
            "start": "500.577"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, in desperate need\nfor a solution to all of this,", 
            "dur": "4.128", 
            "start": "502.943"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought, &quot;What can I do?&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.884", 
            "start": "507.071"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I thought, &quot;Well, why don&#39;t I do\nwhat other women do?", 
            "dur": "3.902", 
            "start": "510.955"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They do it, and it works for them,\neven if it&#39;s temporary.", 
            "dur": "2.077", 
            "start": "514.857"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why don&#39;t I try it?", 
            "dur": "1.859", 
            "start": "516.934"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why don&#39;t I sit in Eva&#39;s chair?&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.654", 
            "start": "518.793"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;What would Eva say to me\nif I apologized to Eva?&quot;", 
            "dur": "3.287", 
            "start": "522.447"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I know. It sounds cheesy. I know.", 
            "dur": "3.56", 
            "start": "526.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it&#39;s actually very scary.", 
            "dur": "2.458", 
            "start": "532.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the reason why I didn&#39;t even want\nto finish this TED talk to begin with.", 
            "dur": "3.999", 
            "start": "534.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because it&#39;s what I know I need to do.", 
            "dur": "3.661", 
            "start": "538.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Eva, stop saying that about your eyes.", 
            "dur": "4.003", 
            "start": "549.122"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have your mother&#39;s eyes,", 
            "dur": "1.738", 
            "start": "553.125"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you would never think for a second", 
            "dur": "1.686", 
            "start": "554.863"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that this woman who gave you life\nand wisdom was not measuring up.", 
            "dur": "5.848", 
            "start": "556.549"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Okay, stop.\nEva, stop saying that about your nose.", 
            "dur": "4.998", 
            "start": "562.397"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have your father&#39;s\nand grandmama&#39;s nose.", 
            "dur": "4.05", 
            "start": "567.395"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yes, your Italian genes are prominent,", 
            "dur": "4.132", 
            "start": "571.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but so is your spirit because of it!", 
            "dur": "3.123", 
            "start": "575.577"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you can identify the notes\nof a lush, jammy Primitivo wine", 
            "dur": "3.995", 
            "start": "578.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "better than most because of it, probably.", 
            "dur": "3.542", 
            "start": "582.695"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, I guess I&#39;m deciding", 
            "dur": "3.574", 
            "start": "590.989"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that if lining my eyes brings symmetry\nto my face and to my mind,", 
            "dur": "6.232", 
            "start": "594.563"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then I guess I&#39;ll do it.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "600.795"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if adding a touch of color to my lips", 
            "dur": "2.762", 
            "start": "602.545"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "allows me to bring joy and color\nto my speech --", 
            "dur": "3.066", 
            "start": "605.307"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then why the heck not?", 
            "dur": "2.051", 
            "start": "608.373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if adding light reflection to my skin\ngives me the little boost of confidence", 
            "dur": "4.878", 
            "start": "610.424"
        }, 
        {
